[The reference to "tropical mosquitos" is in need of clarification. So far, SBV has been detected only in midges (culicoides). However, the entomological aspects of this disease are clearly in need of further research.

The location of the case described is shown on the updated FVO SBV map, available at http://www.bvet.admin.ch/gesundheit_tiere/01065/04051/index.html?lang=de.

Neighbouring countries to the east of infected zones in Germany and Switzerland have not reported SBV so far. - Mod.AS

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: http://healthmap.org/r/1AFv.]
